description.string: Spear phishing attacks target individuals with highly tailored emails that appears to be coming from a co-work or someone they know and trust, making it difficult to avoid opening attachments, clicking on infected links, or replying to attackers with personal or confidential information. Learn how to protect yourself by applying the strategies learned from this short video. Course Duration: 1 min.
